Subject: aha152x: add missing ISA PNP IDs
Git-commit: 50f87f910db0f6dcd3eb569e76c4a48c5315198c
References: bnc#722640
Patch-Mainline: 3.1-rc7

Add ISA PNP IDs of the following cards to aha152x driver:
AVA-1502
AVA-1505
AHA-1510
AVA-1515
AHA-1520
AHA-1522
AHA-1530
AHA-1532
AIC-6360
(list from SCSI.INF file)

This makes my AHA-1530P card (has ADP3015 ID) work automatically.

